query.sql: select HD_DEMO_SK, HD_VEHICLE_COUNT, HD_BUY_POTENTIAL, HD_DEP_COUNT, concat(cast(IB_LOWER_BOUND as string), ' - ', cast (IB_UPPER_BOUND as string)) as income_band from tpcds_10tb.INCOME_BAND, tpcds_10tb.HOUSEHOLD_DEMOGRAPHICS where IB_INCOME_BAND_SK = HD_INCOME_BAND_SK

column.name: Morning Time Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN T_HOUR = 8 AND T_MINUTE >= 30 THEN '08:30 to 09:00' WHEN T_HOUR = 9 AND T_MINUTE < 30 THEN '09:00 to 09:30' WHEN T_HOUR = 9 AND T_MINUTE >= 30 THEN '09:30 to 10:00' WHEN T_HOUR = 10 AND T_MINUTE < 30 THEN '10:00 to 10:30' WHEN T_HOUR = 10 AND T_MINUTE >= 30 THEN '10:30 to 11:00' WHEN T_HOUR = 11 AND T_MINUTE < 30 THEN '11:00 to 11:30' WHEN T_HOUR = 11 AND T_MINUTE >= 30 THEN '11:30 to 12:00' WHEN T_HOUR = 12 AND T_MINUTE < 30 THEN '12:00 to 12:30' ELSE 'Other' END

column.name: Catalog Sales Price Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN CS_SALES_PRICE BETWEEN 0 AND 500 THEN '500 or Less' ELSE 'More than 500' END

column.name: YEAR_MONTH
column.sql: CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(D_DATE AS string),1,4), '-', SUBSTRING(CAST(D_DATE AS string),6,2),'-01') AS DATE)

column.name: YEAR_WEEK
column.sql: CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(D_DATE AS STRING),1,4), '-', SUBSTRING(CAST(D_DATE AS STRING),6,2), '-', LPAD(CAST(D_WEEK_SEQ AS STRING), 2, '0'))

column.name: YEAR_QUARTER
column.sql: CAST(CONCAT(SUBSTRING(CAST(D_DATE AS STRING),1,4), '-', LPAD(TRIM(D_QOY), 2, '0'), '-01') AS DATE)

query.sql: SELECT customer_sk, sold_year, CASE WHEN total_catalog > total_non_catalog THEN 1 ELSE 0 END catalog_preferred FROM ( SELECT customer_sk, sold_year, SUM( CASE WHEN sale_type IN ('c') THEN year_total ELSE 0 END) total_catalog, SUM( CASE WHEN sale_type IN ('s', 'w') THEN year_total ELSE 0 END) total_non_catalog FROM ( SELECT ss_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 's' sale_type, SUM(((ss_ext_list_price-ss_ext_wholesale_cost-ss_ext_discount_amt)+ ss_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM tpcds_10tb.store_sales, tpcds_10tb.date_dim WHERE ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY ss_customer_sk, d_year UNION ALL SELECT ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 'w' sale_type, SUM(((ws_ext_list_price-ws_ext_wholesale_cost-ws_ext_discount_amt)+ ws_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM tpcds_10tb.web_sales, tpcds_10tb.date_dim WHERE ws_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY ws_bill_customer_sk, d_year UNION ALL SELECT cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk, d_year sold_year, 'c' sale_type, SUM(((cs_ext_list_price-cs_ext_wholesale_cost-cs_ext_discount_amt)+ cs_ext_sales_price)/2) year_total FROM tpcds_10tb.catalog_sales, tpcds_10tb.date_dim WHERE cs_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk GROUP BY cs_bill_customer_sk, d_year) t GROUP BY customer_sk, sold_year) z
SELECT p.*, ss.* FROM tpcds_10tb.promotion p INNER JOIN tpcds_10tb.store_sales ss ON ss.ss_promo_sk = p.p_promo_sk

SELECT ss.*, sr.*, case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 30) then '<= 30 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 30) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 60) then '31-60 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 60) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 90) then '61-90 days' when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 90) and (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 120) then '91-120 days' else '> 120 days' end as returns_time_tier, 1 as returns_count FROM tpcds_10tb.store_returns sr INNER JOIN tpcds_10tb.store_sales ss ON ss.ss_ticket_number = sr.sr_ticket_number AND ss.ss_item_sk = sr.sr_item_sk AND ss.ss_customer_sk = sr.sr_customer_sk

column.name: Sales Price Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN SS_SALES_PRICE > 200 THEN '200 and More' WHEN SS_SALES_PRICE BETWEEN 150 AND 200 THEN '150-200' WHEN SS_SALES_PRICE BETWEEN 100 AND 150 THEN '100-150' WHEN SS_SALES_PRICE BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN ' 50-100' ELSE ' 50 and Less' END

column.name: Net Profit Tier
column.sql: CASE WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT > 25000 THEN 'More than 25000' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 3000 AND 25000 THEN '3000-25000' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 2000 AND 3000 THEN '2000-3000' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 300 AND 2000 THEN '300-2000' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 250 AND 300 THEN '250-300' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 200 AND 250 THEN '200-250' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 150 AND 200 THEN '150-200' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 100 AND 150 THEN '100-150' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 50 AND 100 THEN ' 50-100' WHEN SS_NET_PROFIT BETWEEN 0 AND 50 THEN ' 0- 50' ELSE ' 50 or Less' END
